Note the inconsistent indentation... this is odd. Let me look at `_createClearStartAtext(rev)` - it calls `_createClearAuthorship(rev)` which creates a changeset with builder. Then `applyToAText` is called.

But wait - looking at the `_createClearAuthorship` at line 82-91:
